522
00:57:19,840 --> 00:57:20,680
HE FORCES HIS WIFE INTO PROSTITUTION?

523
00:57:20,760 --> 00:57:23,360
<i>You have a girlfriend, a sister,</i>

524
00:57:24,400 --> 00:57:25,440
<i>a mother.</i>

525
00:57:26,920 --> 00:57:28,320
<i>How could you do this to me?</i>

526
00:57:28,400 --> 00:57:30,480
<i>But you're not them.</i>

527
00:57:34,280 --> 00:57:35,960
<i>If you don't want trouble…</i>

528
00:57:36,040 --> 00:57:37,480
HOW DID HE DO THIS? HORRIBLE.

529
00:57:37,560 --> 00:57:38,720
WHAT IS THIS GUY'S HEART MADE OF?

530
00:57:38,800 --> 00:57:40,520
<i>…maybe learn to behave better.</i>

531
00:57:40,600 --> 00:57:43,720
Mr. Mahasamut,
is the man in the clip really you?

532
00:57:43,800 --> 00:57:45,760
Yes, please answer.

533
00:57:45,840 --> 00:57:48,640
You blackmailed Ms. Palida
and forced her into prostitution,

534
00:57:48,720 --> 00:57:50,040
even though she wasn't even your employee.

535
00:57:50,120 --> 00:57:53,200
You're an MP. You represent the people.
How could you do this?

536
00:57:53,280 --> 00:57:54,720
Yes. How could you?

537
00:57:54,800 --> 00:57:55,920
Tell us.

538
00:57:56,000 --> 00:57:57,960
Tell us the truth.

539
00:57:58,800 --> 00:58:02,000
Before becoming Prime Minister,
become a decent human being first.

540
00:58:02,080 --> 00:58:03,320
Yes.

541
00:58:03,400 --> 00:58:05,720
How could you do this?

542
00:58:05,800 --> 00:58:07,600
Wait, wait. I'm being framed.

543
00:58:09,320 --> 00:58:11,760
I'm not answering any questions.

544
00:58:11,840 --> 00:58:13,640
If there's anything,
we'll settle it in court.

545
00:58:13,720 --> 00:58:14,560
Oh?

546
00:58:14,640 --> 00:58:18,160
Everyone, please stop.

547
00:58:18,240 --> 00:58:20,200
We'll verify the information first,

548
00:58:20,280 --> 00:58:22,120
and we'll arrange
another press conference afterward.

549
00:58:33,000 --> 00:58:34,200
Go, go.

550
00:58:39,680 --> 00:58:40,520
Why did you stop?

551
00:58:51,240 --> 00:58:52,480
This is the police.

552
00:58:53,280 --> 00:58:55,960
Mr. Mahasamut Pasukampanart,

553
00:58:56,040 --> 00:58:57,960
step out and give your statement
to the authorities.

554
00:58:58,040 --> 00:59:00,160
You are under arrest

555
00:59:00,240 --> 00:59:03,520
for intimidation, coercion, assault,

556
00:59:03,600 --> 00:59:06,760
forced prostitution, corruption,

557
00:59:06,840 --> 00:59:09,040
and murder with destruction of evidence.

558
00:59:09,120 --> 00:59:11,120
Oh, Mr. DP,

559
00:59:11,200 --> 00:59:14,000
how many crimes have you committed?

560
00:59:14,080 --> 00:59:15,000
HE DESERVES THE DEATH PENALTY

561
00:59:15,080 --> 00:59:16,600
Gotta hand it to him.

562
00:59:16,680 --> 00:59:18,840
He's evil.

563
00:59:18,920 --> 00:59:21,200
Will the police really be able
to put him in prison?

564
00:59:21,280 --> 00:59:23,080
If he slips away again,

565
00:59:24,320 --> 00:59:26,000
I'll kill him with my own hands.

566
00:59:26,080 --> 00:59:27,200
Surrender yourselves.

567
00:59:27,840 --> 00:59:28,800
Run over them.

568
00:59:28,880 --> 00:59:30,200
Hey! Stop!

569
00:59:30,280 --> 00:59:33,160
- Move!
- Stop!

570
00:59:33,760 --> 00:59:34,840
Move! Go!

571
00:59:36,400 --> 00:59:38,480
- Block the way.
- Fire!

572
00:59:41,200 --> 00:59:42,520
Get out of the vehicle.

573
00:59:44,400 --> 00:59:46,640
Open the door. Open it.

574
00:59:51,680 --> 00:59:52,600
Open it.

575
00:59:53,640 --> 00:59:54,720
Open the door.

576
01:00:19,280 --> 01:00:20,600
Where is Mahasamut?

577
01:00:33,400 --> 01:00:36,040
Dad, can you hear me?

578
01:00:36,120 --> 01:00:38,080
Dad? Dad.

579
01:00:38,680 --> 01:00:40,240
Dad! Dad!

580
01:00:41,120 --> 01:00:42,440
<i>I'm sorry…</i>

581
01:00:43,440 --> 01:00:45,280
I'm truly sorry
for everything that happened.

582
01:00:53,480 --> 01:00:54,920
A netizen just sent this in.

583
01:00:55,000 --> 01:00:57,680
Looking at these two locations,
it has to be him.

584
01:01:02,880 --> 01:01:04,080
Wayu.

585
01:01:04,160 --> 01:01:05,560
How does Wayu know about this?

586
01:01:05,640 --> 01:01:08,280
- Who the hell are you?
- I'm the guy you pointed a gun at.

587
01:01:09,440 --> 01:01:10,240
Raka?

588
01:01:14,160 --> 01:01:15,880
Please don't die, Raka.

589
01:01:15,960 --> 01:01:18,360
Oh my God, is someone
actually going to die here?

590
01:02:14,640 --> 01:02:17,520
Subtitle translation by: Panuwat Baikeawon
